Mijanou Bardot https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mijanou_Bardot 0 Marie-Jeanne Bardot (born on 5 May 1938 in Paris) is a French actress and writer. She starred in the 1960 film Sex Kittens Go to College with Mamie van Doren.She is married to Patrick Bauchau, and lives in Los Angeles. Mijanou is the younger sister of Brigitte Bardot.
